4w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff24fc628-018d-4210-b6ed-0c466224f500_941x529.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff24fc628-018d-4210-b6ed-0c466224f500_941x529.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ff24fc628-018d-4210-b6ed-0c466224f500_941x529.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://www.nathanielbullard.com/presentations">纳特·布拉德（Nat Bullard）</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>中国是这里最重要的球员，因为它几乎是世界上唯一建造新燃煤电厂的国家，而且它正在建造很多国家。我建议对劳里·迈尔利维尔塔（Lauri Myllyvirta）的出色采访，即尽管中国已经付诸实施了如此多的可再生能源，但中国已经付出的排放量仍在上升： </p><div class="embedded-post-wrap" data-attrs="{&quot;id&quot;:143212794,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.volts.wtf/p/whats-going-on-with-china-these-days&quot;,&quot;publication_id&quot;:193024,&quot;publication_name&quot;:&quot;Volts&quot;,&quot;publication_logo_url&quot;:&quot;https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4612151e-5cad-4006-b84b-66d629fd7fde_1024x1024.png&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;What's going on with China these days? &quot;,&quot